precept Test

field counter as integer
field events as log of string
field test as timezone default 'America/Toronto'
field test2 as instant default '2026-05-16T14:30:00Z'
field test25 as zoneddatetime default '2026-05-16T14:30:00[America/Toronto]'
field test3 as quantity default '25 km/h'
field test4 as unitofmeasure default test3.unit

state off initial, running
event create initial, start, stop, reset

on create
    -> set counter = 0

from off on start
    -> set counter = counter + 1
    -> add events "{now()}:  started"
    -> transition running

from running on stop
    -> add events "{now()}:  stopped"
    -> transition off

from off, running on reset
    -> set counter = 0
    -> clear events
    -> no transition